  "title": "Temp Pharmacy Assistant (3-6 months, #HKN)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: West</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $10-$11 per hour</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in pharmacy operations</li><li>Help to deliver/top up medications for satellite pharmacy</li><li>Ensure accurate reading and interpretation of prescription</li><li>Ensure accurate quality check when processing of prescriptions - checking on validity, keying, packing and labelling</li><li>Assist in pre-packing of medication/prescriptions</li><li>Maintaining a high standard of cleanliness and tidiness at the work area and storerooms</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p><ul><li>Minimum requirement of GCE \"N/O/A\" Level</li><li>Able to start in short notice</li><li>Able to work long term</li><li>Able to stand for long hours</li><li>Able to carry weight up to 12kg</li><li>5.5 days, office hours</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please send your resume in Word document to <strong>clinicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong> (cc: <a href=\"mailto:kylie@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">kylie@recruitexpress.com.sg</a>)</p><p><br /></p><p>Kylie Ng Kai Wi (R1104775) #HKN</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA Licence No: 99C4599</p><p>Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p>",
